  fhir:StructureDefinition.description [ fhir:value "Documents a medication the patient reports currently taking (eHistory.12 Current Medications), with dose (eHistory.13/.14), route (eHistory.15), and frequency (eHistory.20). Distinct from EMSMedicationAdministration, which records medications administered during the EMS encounter. One resource per reported medication."] ;
